Description.value: The Coronavirus Disease Ontology(CovidO) is a ontology to describle the coronavirus disease in all possible aspect. The CovidO is developed to provide standardized human- and computer-interpretable annotation and representation of various coronavirus information.

subject.value: CovidO: An ontology that cover all the aspects of coronavirus disease.

publisher.value: National Institute of Technology, Kurukshetra, Haryana, India
